text: Sweet memory, still living in my heart,  those memories of you always on my mind.
You have to go I know it’s not your fault,  because you don’t love me any more.
Long lonely nights I’m still thinking of you.  Your cold-cold heart now belongs to other guy.
Still loving you, you are my every thing.  Even though you don’t love me any more.
Please give me another chance  I’ll bring you a Thousand Roses.
Just give us another try. I’ll promise with Thousand Roses.
I’ll give you all my loving and I never ever let you go again….
